description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'HIIT Elliptical Foward/Backwards Intervals: Low Impact Cross Trainer Workout' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: HIIT Elliptical Foward/Backwards Intervals: Low Impact Workout 
#elliptical #lowimpactworkout #crosstrainer 

Join Julia for this low impact elliptical (sometimes called a Cross Trainer) workout structured around 3 min alternating backward and forward intervals. Julia keeps the incline constant at 7%, while progressively increasing resistance.
